{"tid":589160,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】HR教你搵工點叫價","createTime":"2018-03-11T17:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T09:40:30.000Z","uid":70274,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b9862a34225e899da24d26871f9583b2edafedbc","tid":589160,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:02:26.000Z","msg":"打工仔俾人壓價情況時有聽聞，好多時唔係心水價accept咗個offer，先至揼心口；又或者以為自己拎咗個好offer，事後先發現仍然低過市價。唔想追悔莫及？小編有個HR朋友教大家幾招試下，睇下會唔會有助叫價。 <br />\n<br />\n1.用linkedin chok 人事中介人工<br />\n當你開咗linkedin，周不時都會有人事中介搵你過檔，佢地一般會問你apply咗某份工未，呢個時候記得話自己未apply，然後打電話俾中介索吓僱主請人的心水價位，「打完個底」再叫價，咁就唔怕自己開價開得低，增加成功率。 <br />\n<br />\n2.用公營機構的薪酬表做指標<br />\n打工仔千祈唔好有一個錯覺，以為公營機構人工好高，唔可以用來做市價參考。事實上，近呢十年成立的公營機構，好多時候都調返轉，參考私營市場人工，再釐訂機構唔同職級人工。只要你勤力啲google，或者有恆心啲睇返一啲立法會的公開文件，你就會搵到唔少公營機構的薪酬表。望住個表，去返私營公司叫價，得咗！ <br />\n<br />\n3.唔寫current salary，改寫remuneration package<br />\n當打工仔開價在「明」、人事部暗盤價在「暗」的大前提下，求職者一定要出招保障自己。用較高的remuneration package作為起跳價就最好，計埋約滿酬金、花紅同津貼，點都有著數。 <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇打工仔可以分享叫價招數呀？"},{"pid":"0fec8c5ce5f018f134b9fce7cc406adca5b42672","tid":589160,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:34:26.000Z","msg":"第三點唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670c902e7391f0384f875993640d40b442c0002c","tid":589160,"uid":18566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0fec8c5ce5f018f134b9fce7cc406adca5b42672","tid":589160,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:34:26.000Z","msg":"第三點唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"寫曬d乜9 allowance呀bonus呀落去呀公司有保險呀醫療卡呀乜柒都寫曬落去<br />\n有d hr出offer比你出撚到好似同nowtv續約咁平均月費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4e8ce6ccdc97ab1aba4f5d59e0a0c489f74aeb","tid":589160,"uid":75692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"唔寫current salary 得咩?<br />\n班友實問"},{"pid":"65a949813aa1c99ad46a587962d151f04fa7def2","tid":589160,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"670c902e7391f0384f875993640d40b442c0002c","tid":589160,"uid":18566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0fec8c5ce5f018f134b9fce7cc406adca5b42672","tid":589160,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:34:26.000Z","msg":"第三點唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"寫曬d乜9 allowance呀bonus呀落去呀公司有保險呀醫療卡呀乜柒都寫曬落去<br />\n有d hr出offer比你出撚到好似同nowtv續約咁平均月費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"咁如果而家份工係過渡工作（性質同本行冇關係）<br />\n人工低<br />\n咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見番本行會被人壓？"},{"pid":"c9c485c23f987c7c0a802cb70973185f6c47faa3","tid":589160,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65a949813aa1c99ad46a587962d151f04fa7def2","tid":589160,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"670c902e7391f0384f875993640d40b442c0002c","tid":589160,"uid":18566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0fec8c5ce5f018f134b9fce7cc406adca5b42672","tid":589160,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:34:26.000Z","msg":"第三點唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"寫曬d乜9 allowance呀bonus呀落去呀公司有保險呀醫療卡呀乜柒都寫曬落去<br />\n有d hr出offer比你出撚到好似同nowtv續約咁平均月費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:48